Network Use Provision (AGPL-3.0 Specific)
===============================================================================

If you run a modified version of this API on a server and let other users
communicate with it there, your server must also allow them to download the
source code corresponding to the modified version running there.

This means that if you use OpenJornada API as a web service (SaaS), you must
provide access to the source code, including any modifications you have made.

