Third-Party Dependencies (API)
===============================================================================

This component includes or depends on the following open-source libraries:

Core Framework:
- FastAPI (0.104.1) - MIT License
  https://github.com/tiangolo/fastapi

Database:
- Motor (3.3.1) - Apache License 2.0
  https://github.com/mongodb/motor
- PyMongo (4.5.0) - Apache License 2.0
  https://github.com/mongodb/mongo-python-driver

Authentication & Security:
- PyJWT (2.8.0) - MIT License
  https://github.com/jpadilla/pyjwt
- Python-jose (3.3.0) - MIT License
  https://github.com/mpdavis/python-jose
- Passlib (1.7.4) - BSD License
  https://passlib.readthedocs.io/
- Bcrypt (4.0.1) - Apache License 2.0
  https://github.com/pyca/bcrypt

Data Validation:
- Pydantic (2.4.2) - MIT License
  https://github.com/pydantic/pydantic

HTTP Client:
- HTTPX (0.25.0) - BSD License
  https://github.com/encode/httpx

Utilities:
- Python-multipart (0.0.6) - Apache License 2.0
  https://github.com/andrew-d/python-multipart
- Python-dotenv (1.0.0) - BSD License
  https://github.com/theskumar/python-dotenv

Excel Export:
- OpenPyXL (3.1.2) - MIT License
  https://openpyxl.readthedocs.io/

ASGI Server:
- Uvicorn (0.24.0) - BSD License
  https://github.com/encode/uvicorn

All third-party licenses are compatible with AGPL-3.0 and are included
in their respective dependency packages.

